as sub-pixel rendering variance; allow slightly higher threshold\"\n\n**Cross-cutting Patterns:**\n- All tests wait for selector with 5000-10000ms timeout\n- Animation freeze CSS injected after interactions to stabilize UI\n- Console error collection with NOISE_PATTERNS filtering (401, 403, 429, favicon, ERR_CONNECTION_REFUSED, etc.)\n\n---\n\n### 2. Fixture/Helper Setup\n\n**Main Fixture: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts` (124 lines)**\n\nExtended Playwright `test` with custom `stablePage` fixture providing:\n\n**(a) Deterministic Random Seeds:**\n- Implements Mulberry32 seeded PRNG with seed=42\n- Overrides `Math.random()` for deterministic sequences\n- Overrides `crypto.getRandomValues()` for deterministic Keypair generation\n- Freezes `Date.now()` to fixed timestamp: `1767225600000` (2026-01-01T00:00:00Z)\n\n**(b) Animation/Transition Freezing:**\n```css\n*, *::before, *::after {\n  animation-duration: 0s !important;\n  animation-delay: 0s !important;\n  transition-duration: 0s !important;\n  transition-delay: 0s !important;\n  scroll-behavior: auto !important;\n}\nsvg { animation-play-state: paused !important; }\n```\n- Injected via `addStyleTag()` after each navigation\n- SVG SMIL animations paused via `svg.pauseAnimations()`\n\n**(c) Deterministic Page Load:**\n- Wrapped `page.goto()` to always wait for `networkidle`\n- Waits for `document.fonts.ready` after navigation\n- Executes 300ms settle time for remaining paints\n\n**(d) Console Error Collection:**\n- Listens to `page.on(\"console\", ...)` events\n- Filters noise patterns (auth errors, favicon, connection refused, rate limits)\n- Fails test if non-noise console errors detected\n\n**(e) Export:** `export { expect }` from Playwright\n\n---\n\n### 3. Playwright Visual Test Config\n\n**Main Config: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts` (49 lines)**\n\n```typescript\n// Visual test specific settings:\nsnapshotPathTemplate: \"{testDir}/__snapshots__/{testFilePath}/{arg}{ext}\"\nexpect.toHaveScreenshot.maxDiffPixelRatio: 0.015  // 1.5% tolerance\n\n// Determinism settings:\ntestDir: \"./e2e\"\nfullyParallel: true\nworkers: 1\nretries: 0\n\n// Browser settings:\nviewport: { width: 1280, height: 1080 }\ndevices: Desktop Chrome\n\n// Web server:\nVITE_MOCK_MODE: \"true\"  // Critical: runs with mocked backend\nPLAYWRIGHT_PLATFORM_PORT: 3000 (default)\n```\n\n**Other Configs:**\n- `playwright.local.config.ts`: Local E2E (real wallet, `VITE_MOCK_MODE: false`, port 3002)\n- `playwright.devnet.config.ts`: Devnet E2E (real wallet, `VITE_MOCK_MODE: false`, port 3003, longer timeouts for VRF)\n\n---\n\n### 4. Baselines Directory Structure\n\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/`\n\n**routes.spec.ts baselines (15 images):**\n```\n404.png                 (94 KB, Feb 28)\nclose-call.png          (108 KB, Mar 18)\nclose-call-round.png    (89 KB, Mar 18)\ncoinflip.png            (110 KB, Mar 17)\ncrash.png               (134 KB, Mar 14)\nfairness.png            (203 KB, Feb 28)\ngame-of-trades.png      (112 KB, Feb 28)\nhome.png                (292 KB, Feb 28)\nleaderboard.png         (94 KB, Feb 28)\nloot.png                (90 KB, Feb 28)\nlord-of-rngs.png        (110 KB, Mar 17)\nprofile.png             (91 KB, Feb 28)  ← Profile route baseline\nquests.png              (106 KB, Feb 28)\n```\n\n**states.spec.ts baselines (13 images):**\n```\nclosecall-connected.png         (111 KB, Mar 18)\nclosecall-disconnected.png      (108 KB, Mar 18)\ncoinflip-connected.png          (113 KB, Mar 17)\ncoinflip-disconnected.png       (110 KB, Mar 17)\ncoinflip-error-toast-position.png (113 KB, Mar 17)\nhome-connected.png              (295 KB, Feb 28)\nhome-disconnected.png           (292 KB, Feb 28)\nlotr-back-to-lobby.png          (110 KB, Mar 17)\nlotr-lobby-disconnected.png     (110 KB, Mar 17)\nlotr-tier-connected.png         (113 KB, Mar 17)\nlotr-tier-