n### 2. Fixture/Helper Setup\n\n**Main Fixture: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts` (124 lines)**\n\nExtended Playwright `test` with custom `stablePage` fixture providing:\n\n**(a) Deterministic Random Seeds:**\n- Implements Mulberry32 seeded PRNG with seed=42\n- Overrides `Math.random()` for deterministic sequences\n- Overrides `crypto.getRandomValues()` for deterministic Keypair generation\n- Freezes `Date.now()` to fixed timestamp: `1767225600000` (2026-01-01T00:00:00Z)\n\n**(b) Animation/Transition Freezing:**\n```css\n*, *::before, *::after {\n  animation-duration: 0s !important;\n  animation-delay: 0s !important;\n  transition-duration: 0s !important;\n  transition-delay: 0s !important;\n  scroll-behavior: auto !important;\n}\nsvg { animation-play-state: paused !important; }\n```\n- Injected via `addStyleTag()` after each navigation\n- SVG SMIL animations paused via `svg.pauseAnimations()`\n\n**(c) Deterministic Page Load:**\n- Wrapped `page.goto()` to always wait for `networkidle`\n- Waits for `document.fonts.ready` after navigation\n- Executes 300ms settle time for remaining paints\n\n**(d) Console Error Collection:**\n- Listens to `page.on(\"console\", ...)` events\n- Filters noise patterns (auth errors, favicon, connection refused, rate limits)\n- Fails test if non-noise console errors detected\n\n**(e) Export:** `export { expect }` from Playwright\n\n---\n\n### 3. Playwright Visual Test Config\n\n**Main Config: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts` (49 lines)**\n\n```typescript\n// Visual test specific settings:\nsnapshotPathTemplate: \"{testDir}/__snapshots__/{testFilePath}/{arg}{ext}\"\nexpect.toHaveScreenshot.maxDiffPixelRatio: 0.015  // 1.5% tolerance\n\n// Determinism settings:\ntestDir: \"./e2e\"\nfullyParallel: true\nworkers: 1\nretries: 0\n\n// Browser settings:\nviewport: { width: 1280, height: 1080 }\ndevices: Desktop Chrome\n\n// Web server:\nVITE_MOCK_MODE: \"true\"  // Critical: runs with mocked backend\nPLAYWRIGHT_PLATFORM_PORT: 3000 (default)\n```\n\n**Other Configs:**\n- `playwright.local.config.ts`: Local E2E (real wallet, `VITE_MOCK_MODE: false`, port 3002)\n- `playwright.devnet.config.ts`: Devnet E2E (real wallet, `VITE_MOCK_MODE: false`, port 3003, longer timeouts for VRF)\n\n---\n\n### 4. Baselines Directory Structure\n\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/`\n\n**routes.spec.ts baselines (15 images):**\n```\n404.png                 (94 KB, Feb 28)\nclose-call.png          (108 KB, Mar 18)\nclose-call-round.png    (89 KB, Mar 18)\ncoinflip.png            (110 KB, Mar 17)\ncrash.png               (134 KB, Mar 14)\nfairness.png            (203 KB, Feb 28)\ngame-of-trades.png      (112 KB, Feb 28)\nhome.png                (292 KB, Feb 28)\nleaderboard.png         (94 KB, Feb 28)\nloot.png                (90 KB, Feb 28)\nlord-of-rngs.png        (110 KB, Mar 17)\nprofile.png             (91 KB, Feb 28)  ← Profile route baseline\nquests.png              (106 KB, Feb 28)\n```\n\n**states.spec.ts baselines (13 images):**\n```\nclosecall-connected.png         (111 KB, Mar 18)\nclosecall-disconnected.png      (108 KB, Mar 18)\ncoinflip-connected.png          (113 KB, Mar 17)\ncoinflip-disconnected.png       (110 KB, Mar 17)\ncoinflip-error-toast-position.png (113 KB, Mar 17)\nhome-connected.png              (295 KB, Feb 28)\nhome-disconnected.png           (292 KB, Feb 28)\nlotr-back-to-lobby.png          (110 KB, Mar 17)\nlotr-lobby-disconnected.png     (110 KB, Mar 17)\nlotr-tier-connected.png         (113 KB, Mar 17)\nlotr-tier-selected.png          (110 KB, Mar 17)\nprofile-connected.png           (123 KB, Feb 28)  ← Profile state baseline\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Profile Page Route & Visual Structure\n\n**Route Definition:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx`\n```typescript\n<Route path=\"/profile\" element={<ProfilePage />} />\n```\n\n**ProfilePage Component Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfilePage.tsx` (303 lines)\n\n**Key Features:**\n- **Header Section:**\n  - Avatar (clickable to open selector modal) with edit hint icon\n  - Username display with inline edit (pencil icon → edit/check/cancel icons)\n  - Level progress bar (calls `LevelProgressBar` component)\n  - Optional RNG Buff indicator (gold star icon + timer) - conditional on `hasRNGBuff`\n\n- **Tabs:** Statistics | Transactions | Settings\n  - Tab buttons with active state styling\n  - Content switches based on `activeTab` state\n\n- **Content Areas:**\n  - **Statistics:** `<ProfileStats>` component with aggregate stats grid (6 cards: games played, total wagered, wins, net profit, win rate, best streak) + per-game breakdown table\n  - **Transactions:** `<ProfileTransactions>` component\n  - **Settings:** `<ProfileSettings>` component\n\n- **States Handled:**\n  - `loading`: Shows \"Loading profile...\"\n  - `!myProfile` (disconnected wallet): Shows \"Connect Wallet\" prompt with explanation\n\n- **Styling:** All `.profile-page__*` CSS classes\n\n---\n\n### 6. Visual Baseline Content\n\n**profile.png (routes.spec.ts baseline):**\n- Shows **disconnected state** (wallet not connected)\n- Central message: \"CONNECT WALLET\" with subtitle \"Connect your wallet to view your profile.\"\n- Full page layout with sidebar navigation visible\n- Demonstrates route is accessible but requires wallet connection\n\n**profile-connected.png (states.spec.ts baseline):**\n- Shows **connected wallet state** with Profile filled with data\n- Header displays:\n  - Cyan/blue avatar (procedurally generated \"GU\" monogram for seeded PRNG)\n  - Username: \"DIAMONDSHARK28\"\n  - Level: \"100 /28 / 515.1K XP\" with progress bar\n  - Edit pencil icon visible on username\n- **Statistics Tab Content (currently visible):**\n  - Grid of 6 stat cards: 225 games played, $45.78 total wagered, 133 total wins, +$88.16 net profit (green), 59.1% win rate, 4 best streak\n  - Per-game breakdown table below: Flip You, Jackpot, Crypto Crash, Close Call, Game of Trades (all showing 0 games, 0W/0L, 0%, $0.00)\n- Connected wallet button in top-right corner showing wallet address with dropdown\n- Full page scrollable (notice footer \"TAUNT.\" visible at bottom with FAQ/TERMS/TWITTER/TELEGRAM links)\n\n---\n\n### 7. Summary of Test Patterns\n\n**For Adding Profile Baseline Tests:**\n\n1. **Minimal Route Test** (already exists in routes.spec.ts):\n   - `await stablePage.goto(\"/profile\")`\n   - Takes disconnected baseline snapshot\n   - Already baseline: `profile.png`\n\n2. **State Variant Test** (already exists in states.spec.ts):\n   - Clears wallet state → connects wallet → waits for UI\n   - Uses higher pixel tolerance `0.03` due to avatar SVG rendering\n   - Already baseline: `profile-connected.png`\n\n3. **Test Execution:**\n   - Run visual tests: `pnpm exec playwright test --config=playwright.config.ts`\n   - Update baselines: add `--update-snapshots` flag\n   - Baselines auto-stored in `e2e/__snapshots__/visual/`\n\n4. **Key Gotchas for Profile-Specific Visual Tests:**\n   - Avatar SVG has sub-pixel rendering variance → needs higher tolerance (0.03)\n   - Username input edit state requires interaction testing (clear focus after cancel)\n   - Level progress bar may have gradient rendering variance\n   - RNG Buff indicator (if added) needs animation freeze for SVG star icon\n\n---\n\n**All Files Referenced:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/routes.spec.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/states.spec.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platfor