Event`: \"join\" | \"win\" | \"loss\" | \"refund\"\n\n### **Existing Test Coverage**\n\n1. **Visual regression tests** (in `e2e/visual/states.spec.ts`):\n   - `profile-connected.png` - profile page when wallet is connected\n   - Freezes animations, deterministic fonts, max diff pixel ratio 0.03\n\n2. **Functional E2E test** (in `e2e/local/20-profile-transactions.spec.ts`):\n   - Plays a coinflip match to completion\n   - Navigates to `/profile`\n   - Verifies transaction history appears with 2 rows (join + win/loss)\n   - Verifies game names, event types, amounts, and match deep-links\n   - Tests cursor-based pagination readiness\n\n### **Key Selectors for Visual Testing**\n\n```\n.profile-page                           // Main container\n.profile-page__header                   // Header section\n.profile-page__avatar-section           // Avatar (clickable)\n.profile-page__name                     // Username display\n.profile-page__name-edit                // Username edit mode\n.profile-page__level-section            // Level + buff indicator\n.profile-page__buff-indicator           // RNG Buff pill (when active)\n.profile-page__tabs                     // Tab navigation\n.profile-page__tab                      // Individual tab\n.profile-page__content                  // Content area\n\n.profile-transactions                   // Transactions container\n.profile-transactions__skeleton         // Loading state (5 rows)\n.profile-transactions__empty            // No transactions state\n.profile-transactions__table            // Data table\n.profile-transactions__table tbody tr   // Individual transaction rows\n.profile-transactions__match-link       // Game name link\n.profile-transactions__event            // Event label (join/win/loss/refund)\n.profile-transactions__load-more-btn    // Pagination button\n```\n\nThis comprehensive setup shows the profile page needs coverage for all loading states, empty states, connected states with various tab scenarios, and trans